 Discover how you can efficiently navigate an Instruments trace document, interpret trace data, and record additional profiling data to better understand your specific hang.","type":"text"}]},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC20-10221-Get-your-test-results-faster":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Improve your testing suite to speed up your feedback loop and get fixes in faster. Learn more about the latest improvements to testing in Xcode, including how to leverage test plans, Xcodebuild updates, and APIs to eliminate never-ending and badly-behaved tests. We’ll explore Test Timeouts and Execution Time Allowances in XCTest, examine device parallelization, and detail recommended practices for balancing performance with clear fault localization."}],"role":"sampleCode","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc20-10221-get-your-test-results-faster","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC20-10221-Get-your-test-results-faster","kind":"article","title":"Get your test results faster"},"WWDC19.jpeg":{"type":"image","identifier":"WWDC19.jpeg","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDC19.jpeg","traits":["1x","light"]}],"alt":null},"zntfdr.jpeg":{"type":"image","identifier":"zntfdr.jpeg","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/zntfdr.jpeg","traits":["1x","light"]}],"alt":null},"https://github.com/zntfdr":{"type":"link","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/zntfdr","title":"GitHub","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/zntfdr","titleInlineContent":[{"text":"GitHub","type":"text"}]},"WWDC19-411-spinning":{"type":"image","identifier":"WWDC19-411-spinning","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDC19-411-spinning.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"alt":null},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes":{"type":"topic","title":"WWDC Notes","images":[{"identifier":"WWDCNotes.png","type":"icon"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","abstract":[{"text":"Session notes shared by the community for the community.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/docume